metadata.name: Pepe With a Pearl Earring
metadata.description: The legendary painting "Pepe with a Pearl Earring" - one of the first paintings by Pepelangelo. Painted in January 2017 in St. Petersburg, Russia. Oil on canvas, size 30 Ã— 40cm. This popular painting has been copied many times, printed on T-shirts and so on. But this concrete variant is the very first, the most perfect and the most beloved. The original painting is kept in a private collection in Moscow.
